  Decription:

     Overloads place_design command to run classic flow directive equivalents with advanced flow.

     This command need to be run once to make place_design command to run equvalent directives in advanced flow.

  Example:

     ::xilinx::designutils::enable_equiv_vivado_directives
     place_design -directive AltSpreadLogic_medium -verbose

     ::xilinx::designutils::disable_equiv_vivado_directives

